Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我回俄羅斯去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長谷津棒棒噠 快來玩喲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有走光殺必死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不沒有沒有沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 第2滑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.79,0:23:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個Yuri！？烏托邦之亂
